用到的副程式

subrouting ../utils/barClass.ado

/*
總之就是根據不同的分類結果,顯示某個值得個數或平均
例如有分類結果 y1_1 y1_2(不是0就是1)
barClass y1,over(y1_*) on(mean)
根據不同的分類,計算y1 的平均
沒有ON這個選項,就是計算個數(預設)

*/ 
capture program drop barClass
program barClass
  syntax varname [,over(varlist) on(string)]
  //local fn "tmpx"
  if "`on'"=="" local cmd "count"
  else local cmd "`on'"
  tempfile fn
  foreach class in `over' {
   qui { 
    preserve 
    capture confirm file `fn'
    local ok=_rc

    collapse (`cmd') `varlist' ,by(`class') 

    rename `class' sep
    rename `varlist' `class'
    if `ok'==0 merge 1:1 sep using `fn' ,nogenerate noreport
     save `fn',replace
    restore
    }
  } 

  preserve 
  use `fn',clear
  local idx 1
  foreach item of local over {
   local legend `"`legend' label(`idx' "`cmd' of `item'") "'
   local ++idx
  }
  graph bar `over',over(sep) legend( `legend') blabel(bar) 
  //graph bar `over',over(sep)
  restore

 
end

做法:
合併資料,這一段從panel regression 報告 複製來的

文字

use ../transfer/elder92,clear
set linesize 255
//child
capture safedrop tmp
ren child tmp
recode tmp (5/7=5),gen(child)
capture safedrop tmp
label variable child ""
save ../tmp/tmp,replace

use ../transfer/elder104_v4,clear
append using ../tmp/tmp,gen(year)
replace year = 2015 if year==0
replace year = 2003 if year==1

gen age=age92
replace age=age104 if year==2015
label value age age104


capture safedrop tmp
duplicates report qtype ser_no4
duplicates tag qtype ser_no4,gen(tmp)
drop if tmp==0
egen id=group(qtype ser_no4)
xtset id year

capture safedrop y2015
gen y2015=0
replace y2015=1 if year==2015
 
label define y2015 0 "2003" 1 "2015"
label value y2015 y2015

global xalt2 child2  incom2  
global xalt1 child  incom  
global xcat relin  incsrc mar taba alco spor exam_year sex educ
global xcont  heal  fami  depre money
global xcont100  heal100  fami100  depre100 money100
global xnew dise_o adl_o body_o iadl_o living_o commu_o
global yall y1 y2 y3 y4 y5 y6

esttab using  "`r(fn)'", cells("count(fmt(%9.1f)) mean(fmt(%9.1f)) sd(fmt(%9.1f))") label nowrap  mtitle title("分年") nonumbers unstack noline html
